$$y(n) - 1.1683 y(n-1) + 0.4241 y(n-2) = 0.0640\left(x(n) + 2 x(n-1) + x(n-2)\right)$$

所以有

$$
y(n) = 1.1683 y(n-1) - 0.4241 y(n-2) + 0.0640\left(x(n) + 2 x(n-1) + x(n-2)\right)
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
y(0) &amp;= 0.0640 x(0) \\
&amp;= 0.06420
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
y(1) &amp;= 1.1683y(0) + 0.0640 (2 x(1-1) ) \\
&amp;= 0.2028
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
y(2) &amp;= 1.1683y(1) - 0.4241 y(0) + 0.0640 (x(2-2) ) \\
&amp;= 0.2738
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
y(3) &amp;= 1.1683y(2) - 0.4241 y(1) \\
&amp;= 0.2338
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
y(4) &amp;= 1.1683y(3) - 0.4241 y(2) \\
&amp;= 0.1571
\end{align*}

div.data-content:
故左半平面

$$
\begin{cases}
p_1 &= e^{j \frac{3}{4} \pi} \\
p_2 &= e^{j \frac{5}{4} \pi} \\
\end{cases}
$$

滤波器频响函数

$$
\begin{align*}
H(p) &= \frac{1}{(p - p_1)(p - p_2)} \\
&= \frac {1}{p^2+\sqrt 2 p + 1}
\end{align*}
$$

代入$p = j \lambda = j \frac{\omega}{2 \pi f_p} = \frac{j\omega}{200\pi}$

$$
H(j\omega) = \frac{1}{(\frac{j \omega}{200 \pi})^2 + \frac{\sqrt 2}{200 \pi}j\omega + 1}
$$
